This project is an independently-developed reverse-engineering of the
pre-CS5 Adobe Flash binary FLA file format, created for interoperability
purposes. No Adobe source code or binaries are included or redistributed
in this repository. Contributors who wish to extend the decoder must
obtain their own copy of any reference binaries (e.g. `flash.exe`).

Trademarks
