Prior art and credits
---------------------
- JPEXS Free Flash Decompiler
  https://github.com/jindrapetrik/jpexs-decompiler
  Invaluable reference for the LosslessImageBinDataReader and overall
  SWF/FLA format knowledge.

- Ruffle
  https://github.com/ruffle-rs/ruffle
  Open-source SWF runtime. Its shape rendering helped sanity-check
  coordinate units.

- fla-viewer
  https://github.com/lifeart/fla-viewer
  Handles the post-CS5 XFL/zip format (different from this project's
  scope, but cited for context).

The Ghidra-driven disassembly that enabled this decoder was performed
with the assistance of Claude Code (Anthropic).

